SUMMARY: Bingo Night at Eataly/Birroteca – Limited Spots! 🎉
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n🎉 **
 Bingo Night at Birroteca – Limited Spots!** 🎉\n\nLooking for a fun (a
 nd slightly competitive 😄) way to spend your Tuesday night? Join us for
  **Bingo Night** on **Tuesday\, April 7** at **Birroteca in Eataly (55 Blo
 or St West)**!\n\n🕢 **Bingo starts at 7:30 PM**\n👋 **Colleen will be
  there earlier** — just ask for her table when you arrive and come say h
 i!\nGet ready for a lively evening of laughs\, great food\, and maybe even
  a little beginner’s luck 🍀 if you haven't signed up for trivia with 
 colleen before\, pls. e-transfer a $5 deposit to tommills@rogers.com\,and 
 notify me right away\, on this page\, or the personal msg. page. NOTE - ev
 eryone MUST spend at least $10\, plus tax and tip.\n\n🍝 Check out the m
 enu here:\n[https://www.eataly.ca/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ETO_Birroteca
 _Menu_Main_2026.03.26-1.pdf](https://www.eataly.ca/wp-content/uploads/2024
 /09/ETO_Birroteca_Menu_Main_2026.03.26-1.pdf)\n\n⚠️ **Very limited spo
 ts available** — please respect your RSVP so everyone who signs up can e
 njoy the night.\nCome for the bingo\, stay for the food\, and leave with b
 ragging rights (and maybe a win or two 😉). See you there!
