SUMMARY:🎬 Movie Meetup: 30th Anniversary of Jerry Maguire 🎉. Tuesday
  $7.99 pricing. 
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n🎬 **
 Movie Meetup: 30th Anniversary of *Jerry Maguire*** 🎉\n\nJoin us for a 
 feel-good classic as we celebrate **30 years of heart\, hustle\, and unfor
 gettable quotes** with a special screening of Jerry Maguire!\n📅 **Date:
 ** Tuesday\, April 14\n🕡 **Showtime:** 6:30 PM\n📍 **Location:** Cine
 plex Cinemas Yonge-Dundas\n💲 **Special Tuesday Price:** Just $7.99!\n
 🎟️ **Get tickets here:**\n[https://www.cineplex.com/movie/jerry-magui
 re-30th-anniversary](https://www.cineplex.com/movie/jerry-maguire-30th-ann
 iversary)\n\n***\n\n### 🌟 Why This Night Matters\n\nReleased in 1996 an
 d starring Tom Cruise\, Renée Zellweger\, and Cuba Gooding Jr. (in his Os
 car-winning role)\, *Jerry Maguire* is more than just a sports movie—it
 ’s a story about integrity\, love\, and finding what really matters.\nWi
 th iconic lines like *“Show me the money!”* and *“You had me at hell
 o\,”* this film has become a cultural touchstone. Hitting the **30-year 
 milestone** is the perfect excuse to relive the magic on the big screen wi
 th fellow fans.\n\n***\n\n### 🎥 Movie Details\n\n⏱️ **Runtime:** 2 
 hours 19 minutes (139 minutes)\n▶️ **Watch the trailer:**\n[trailer he
 re](https://youtu.be/KUd3gwaf0KQ?si=VH-Vn7cRe7xIkVrw)\n\n***\n\n### 🙌 M
 eetup Details\n\nNick will be **outside the auditorium before and after th
 e movie** holding a Meetup sign—feel free to say hello\, chat about your
  favorite scenes\, or just soak in the nostalgia together.\n\nWhether it
 ’s your first time watching or your tenth\, this is one of those movies 
 that just hits differently in a theatre. Come celebrate a true classic wit
 h great company! 🍿
