  award-winning comedian Gavin Crawford makes games out of the headlines\, 
 along with a panel of comedians and celebrities.\n\nIt's also become [some
 what of a TikTok hit](https://www.niemanlab.org/2023/10/wait-wait-dont-tel
 l-me-how-this-canadian-radio-show-became-a-tiktok-hit/)\n\nNote - very lim
 ited\, sold out event. **Only sign up if you can 100% commit to attend.**\
 n\nMeet 6PM\nDoors open 6:30PM\nTaping should end around 8:30PM.\n\n**THIS
  GROUP IS OPEN TO THOSE THAT WANT TO BE SOCIAL\, MAKE FRIENDS\, THAT ARE S
